<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Seitz Marschall zu Oberndorf, Viztum in Niederbayern</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Burkhard Hofner, Diener der Stadt, selbst antwortet.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_534" id="266v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l1">Seıcʒen Marſchalck cʒu <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>ndorff</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l2">vıcʒtum in Nẏdernbeẏrn / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> her vicʒtum / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Burckh<ex>art</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l4"> <expan>hofn<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnſers <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wegen vnd <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> er 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu der </del> nu herheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l5"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt So <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir Jn <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan> <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> beſant vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l6">cʒerede geſacʒt vnd der ſpricht Er vvöll ew <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_534_r1l7"><expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd vvo wir etc </ab>
</del><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l8"> <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her vicʒtum / Als vvir ew nehſt von Burkhart hofners </ab><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> dieners der deſmals niht anheim was auf <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief </ab><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l11"><expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo iſt derſelb vnſer diener </ab><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l12"> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> herheim <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd den <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir durch ewren </ab><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l13"><expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> beſant vnd cʒurede geſacʒt / vnd Jn auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief </ab><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l14">hören laſſen / vnd der hat vns <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ Er ew ſelber </del></ab><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l15">
<del rend="strikethrough">auf <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief ein <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan></del> Er wölle ew ſelber ein <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l17">darümb <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd wo vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb vnd dinſt </ab><ab facs="#facs_534_r1l18"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ın <expan>vıg<ex>ilia</ex></expan> <expan>Om<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> <expan>S<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_534" id="266v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Seiczen Marschalck czu <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>ndorff</expan>, vicztum in
                        Nydernbeyrn</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her vicztum, als ir uns
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                    <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Burckh<ex>art</ex></expan>
<expan>Hofn<ex>er</ex>s,</expan> unsers <expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s,</expan>
                            wegen und <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> er nu herheim
                                    <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> besant und cze rede gesaczt und der
                            spricht, er wöll ew <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> ein
                                    <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n;</expan> und wo wir etc.</del>
<expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her vicztum, als wir ew nehst von Burkhart
                        Hofners, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> dieners, der desmals niht anheim
                        was, auf <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief
                            <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also ist derselb unser diener
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> herheim
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und den <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        durch ewren <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> besant und czu rede gesaczt und
                        in auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief hören lassen; und der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, er wölle ew selber ein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darümb
                            <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dinst.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
